title: Radio Row Day 2: Justin Herbert, Marlon Humphrey and Mad Dog Chris Russo
itunes:title: Radio Row Day 2: Justin Herbert, Marlon Humphrey and Mad Dog Chris Russo
description:
A convention center filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal are back on radio row with a whole bunch of superstars! Chargers QB Justin Herbert stops by as well as Ravens CB Marlon Humphrey. Of course we end the show with a Super Bowl week tradition, Mad Dog Chris Russo. If you are afraid of spiders: beware of this episode.
